article.description: — Michael Moreno had 22 points as Eastern Kentucky rolled past NAIA-level Ohio Valley 103-74 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Moreno leads E. Kentucky over Ohio Valley 103-74
article.linkText: Moreno leads E. Kentucky over Ohio Valley 103-74
article.story: RICHMOND, Ky. -- — Michael Moreno had 22 points as Eastern Kentucky rolled past NAIA-level Ohio Valley 103-74 on Thursday night. Russhard Cruickshank had 14 points for Eastern Kentucky (2-0). Braxton Beverly added 13 points. Jomaru Brown had 12 points. Tariq Balogun tied a career high five blocks. Cooper Robb, whose 21.0 points per game entering the contest led the Colonels, finished 1-for-5 shooting. Andre Leavell had 31 points and seven rebounds for the Fighting Scots and Ken Martin scored 14. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
